4. DIRECT DEBITS
4.1. Upon your enrolment on the Platform, you will be required to provide your account information
complete a Direct Debit Mandate form, by which you will arrange how much you intend to invest
in the Fund on a periodic basis (weekly or monthly) and when such investment will be made. With
the direct debit, your Banker automatically deducts a specified amount from your bank account
and credits same to your PayDay Investor Account.
4.2. Direct debits shall only be applied to investments in the Fund and shall, on no account, be applicable
to payment for products purchased on Merchants websites.
